prf_app Namespace Reference

Application side classes expected to be used frequently. More...

Detailed Description

This class presently contains only the ObsHandler and InterfaceBase. These will, in all likelihood, appear frequently in various types of applications. They do not define what PROFASI is, but rather constiture tools for conveniently using the model in an organized manner.
